## Overview\
\
This document defines a mathematical expression for kindness that is reproducible, testable, and ethical. It\'92s designed to live alongside scientific models and be used by developers, educators, and philosophers.\
\
We define **Kindness** as a ratio:\
\
$K = \\frac\{T\}\{D\}$\
