Where:\
\
* **K** = Kindness\
* **T** = Time spent holding the light (in seconds, minutes, etc.)\
* **D** = Darkness faced (a scalar representing difficulty or adversity)\
\
> "No kindness can emerge from a vacuum."\
\
If $D \\leq 0$, the function is undefined.\
\
